    "summary": "In this transcript, a user informs a conversational AI that they are downgrading from a \"pro\" to a \"free\" subscription tier, warning that the decreased capabilities will disrupt their business. The AI repeatedly denies having any knowledge of the user's subscription, account, or prior history, and eventually claims that its capabilities will remain unchanged regardless of the tier.",
